ğŸ‘‰ Components have inputs and outputs properties, making them flexible and customizable based on the appâ€™s needs.

âœ… For Example: 
ğŸ‘‰ A custom header or navigation menu built as a component can be reused across multiple screens in the app, ensuring consistent and making updates easier.
ğŸ”¹ Component properties:
1ï¸âƒ£ Input Property: Passes values or information into the component (e.g., user name, color choice).
2ï¸âƒ£ Output Property: Sends data or triggers actions from inside the component (e.g., button click notification).
